contacts.name: Guinaifen
contacts.signature: Not causing trouble, not fearing trouble, and no crazy challenges

121800000.text: Hey, do you have time right now? Can we meet up at Fyxestroll Garden?

121800001.text: What are you planning to do at Fyxestroll Garden? By the way, are you feeling better now?

121800002.text: Aw, thanks for the concern! People like me, who have to hustle all day out there under the sun, are all pretty tough...

121800003.text: The healers in the Alchemy Commission have looked me over. Besides a bit of shock and some bruises, I'm totally fine!

121800004.text: Isn't Guinaifen supposed to be at the apothecary right now? Don't think you can fool me again, you little heliobus!

121800005.text: Come on, can't we have some trust between us?

121800006.text: The healers in the Alchemy Commission have looked me over. Besides a bit of shock and some bruises, I'm totally fine!

121800007.text: Didn't you cause a lot of trouble last time at Fyxestroll Garden?

121800008.text: I'm terribly sorry for the trouble I caused last time.

121800009.text: But I really need your help this time.

121800010.text: Actually, Hanya personally invited us for a meeting.

121800011.text: Well, why don't you just come to Fyxestroll Garden so we can talk in person? Texting is too much of a hassle.
